  "body": " Updates to json-rpc for 1559\nThis is still somewhat of a moving target with regard to field names for (feeCap and gasPremium) as well as how effectiveGasPrice will be incorporated into transaction receipts.  However, at present these are the list of json-rpc changes for 1559\n* baseFee added to block headers:\n    * eth_getBlockByHash\n    * eth_getBlockByNumber\n    * eth_getUncleByBlockHashAndIndex\n    * eth_getUncleByBlockNumberAndIndex\n* 1559 transaction types, add effectiveGasPrice to receipts for:\n  * eth_getTransactionByHash\n  * eth_getTransactionByBlockHashAndIndex\n  * eth_getTransactionByBlockNumberAndIndex\n* add Optional feeCap and gasPremium:\n    * eth_signTransaction\n    * eth_sendTransaction\n* test_rawImportBlock \n\t* support 1559 transactions \n* test_setChainParameters:\n\t* currentGasLimit overload with currentGasTarget\n\t* add currentBaseFee ",
